( I think I’m quite ready to join the Squad now 😝)

I’ve read it last week and my answers are:

Are DAOs already ready?

Not at all.
Legal challenges are always present.

How does the landscape looks like today?

It’s too early. As the authors say a ‘wait and see’ approach is the best choice.

Will DAOs really going to make it?

Yes sure! And can’t wait to see that day.

DAOs represent a mind shift in how business is done.
It is a system of digital cooperation, where ownership is shared for an economic, political or social purpose.']
